{
  "stem": "11611.6",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Four.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Elliot, James, Nikolas, and Julia.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Reluctantly, one did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My oldest son worked as an economist for years and went to law school in his middle 30s.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Elliot.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But he worked as an economist for Indian tribes on Indian reservations, primarily the northern Cheyenne in Montana.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I think he finally reached the conclusion that it was better to be a lawyer, let's say, working for the Indians than to be an economist.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So he went to law school out west somewhere.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After he'd been in practice for a couple of years on Indian reservations, he went to work for OSI.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "OSI is the Office of Special Investigations, which is a-- a very specialized office in the Department of Justice, US Department of Justice, whose activities consist primarily of investigating Nazis or Nazi accomplices or auxiliaries who entered the United States under false premises, lying and cheating their way through the-- through the barriers to entry, and in many cases, becoming naturalized.",
      "word_count": 61
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "These were people who-- mainly Eastern Europeans, although I think some Germans and Austrians among them-- whom the office investigated with a view to possible deportation and denaturalization, primarily on the ground of fraud.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I do because I was the first director of it and set the office up back in 1979.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By accident.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "How did it happen?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A young partner of mine, with whom I was in good terms, went to work in the Department of Justice.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From Arnold and Porter.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Irv Nathan went to work for Phil Heymann, who was the head of the Criminal Division in the Department of Justice.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One day, Irv called me up and said, we're thinking of setting something up in the department along the lines of OSI.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'79.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably the middle of '79.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
